{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/steam_gif_about_v4.gif?t=1717532683\" /><br>Dark Crown is a roguelike deckbuilder where a fresh take on chess meets magical abilities. Gather your army and a powerful deck to reclaim your kingdom from the shadows.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/draw_card_steam.gif?t=1717532683\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/steam_div_newChess.png?t=1717532683\" /><br>Faster, punchier, and with new rules to the board. Move all your pieces and apply different cards that enhance their abilities to destroy hordes of enemies. But watch out! Every power applies corruption to your pieces, and too much of it can have consequences...<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/steam_gif_chess_v4.gif?t=1717532683\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/steam_div_synergies.png?t=1717532683\" /><br>Utilize a vast deck of skills to combo movement, pieces, and environment. Effects can propagate and interfere with one another, so make the most of their combinations to increase your power.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/steam_gif_cards_v4.gif?t=1717532683\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/steam_div_replayability.png?t=1717532683\" /><br>Expand and personalize your deck. Recruit and enhance your soldiers, creating your own playstyle with every new run.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3021800/extras/steam_gif_pro